Stephen Elliott’s true crime memoir comes to life in The Adderall Diaries starring James Franco, Amber Heard and Christian Slater, just to name a few. The Daily Quirk caught up with director/screenwriter Pamela Romanowsky along with actors Amber Heard and Christian Slater on the red carpet at the Tribeca Film Festival premiere...
